sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant BillingAPI
    participant Stripe
    participant Database

    User->>BillingAPI: POST /invoices/:subscriptionId/ref/:invoiceRefId/pay
    BillingAPI->>Database: Load invoice + customer profile
    BillingAPI->>Stripe: Create Checkout Session
    Stripe-->>BillingAPI: checkoutUrl
    BillingAPI->>Database: Record payment attempt
    BillingAPI-->>User: 200 InitiatePaymentResponse

    User->>Stripe: Complete checkout
    Stripe->>BillingAPI: POST /webhooks/payments/stripe
    BillingAPI->>Database: Idempotent webhook event + mark paid
    BillingAPI-->>Stripe: 200
